{"id": "1417842352642588692", "channel_id": "1417842352642588692", "type": 0, "author_id": "713171670835396639", "author_name": "maririn.g", "author_bot": false, "content": "I've attached my current box below, new to the game and is still trying to figure out what team I want to play with. I'm leaning towards a poison centered team. I have yet to test this but I'm open to suggestions on what team to run.\n\nI also got some standard selectors (3x) and I'm wondering which units I should use them on.\n\nAnd probably the most important factor, once I'm set with a team, I'm wondering where I should pull/who should I save for if there are any certain reruns already laid out.", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T11:59:19.107000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "perfect", "emoji_id": "1356084498630053979", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1417842353598763071", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-09-17-10-15-36-767_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 160516, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417842352642588692/1417842353598763071/Screenshot_2025-09-17-10-15-36-767_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cd0897&is=69cbb717&hm=10e3be91637d86271a60bdbec079dfc63d3047ede5115883960e8b085131285f&"}, {"id": "1417842354169057366", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-09-17-19-53-57-744_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 136395, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1417842352642588692/1417842354169057366/Screenshot_2025-09-17-19-53-57-744_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cd0897&is=69cbb717&hm=c7ba88b496651cac873929f9a22785848af99c2c0100f7bc5fdba2c9bd3207b4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417842352642588692", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team Building, Selectors and Pulling Plan", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1417915730187518144", "channel_id": "1417842352642588692", "type": 0, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "There are two posion teams endgame:\n\n1. 24 Blue. The unit 24 (you don't have) in Chaos with blue is one of the best teams in the endgame. \n\n2. Liz + Lily team. This team you can make right now. But it is one of the harder teams to learn how to play. It's often not recommended to beginners as it can be hard to play.\n\nLiz / Lily / Horla + 1 more unit will work for you.", "timestamp": "2025-09-17T16:50:53.677000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💗", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1417842352642588692", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team Building, Selectors and Pulling Plan", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747088995811358"]}
